Section.name: About ISTS
Section.description:
International School of Technology and Sciences (ISTS) for Women is a private engineering college located at Rajahmundry in East Godavari district of Andhra Pradesh. The college is affiliated to JNTU, Hyderabad and approved by AICTE, New Delhi. The college offers undergraduate courses in engineering in three branches. International School of Technology & Sciences (ISTS) offers a global approach to education and research, with a focus on international perspectives and expertise
